-- BofA rises after analyst comments
-- 
-- Mon May 18, 2009 8:27am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/05/18/us-bofa-idUSTRE54H2JN20090518

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Bank of America Corp ( BAC.N ) rose 7.7 percent to $11.49 in premarket trading on Monday, after some analysts issued positive comments on the stock. 

 Goldman Sachs added it to its conviction buy list. (Reporting by  Ryan Vlastelica ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)